<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    {{>upperlinks}}
    <title>Suggest-Gift</title>
</head>

<body>
    {{>nav}}
    <div class="intro">
        <h1>AI Gift Suggestion Tool</h1>
        <div class="read-word"></div>
        <div class="count-word"></div>
        <p>A cutting-edge tool for helping people choose the ideal present for their loved ones is an AI-powered gift
        recommendation tool.
        Due to the rising demand for AI-based solutions, many businesses are now providing gift recommendation systems that make
        use of the capabilities of artificial intelligence to enhance the personal and pleasant aspects of gift-giving.</p>
        <p>How it works:</p>
        <p>Information about the recipient's preferences, interests, and previous present selections is gathered by the AI-powered
        gift recommendation tool.
        Each recipient's individualised gift recommendation list is made using the information provided.
        The tool considers a variety of elements, such as the recipient's age, gender, interests, and personal style.
        The tool also takes into account the occasion, such as birthdays, anniversaries, or holidays, for which the present is
        being given.</p>
        <p>Benefits of using an AI-powered gift suggestion tool:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Time-saving feature: The AI-powered gift recommendation tool does away with the need to spend hours looking through
            present possibilities.
            A list of suggestions that are suited to the recipient's tastes and requirements is immediately provided by the
            application.</li>
            <li>Personalization: The AI-powered gift suggestion tool may provide recommendations that are specific to each person by
            leveraging data and information about the receiver.</li>
            <li>Convenience: People who are short on time or unable to physically visit a business may find the gift suggestion tool to
            be useful because it can be accessed from anywhere, at any time.</li>
            <li>Increased precision: The AI-powered gift suggestion tool can examine a variety of data to provide precise and
            individualised recommendations.
            This increases customer satisfaction and reduces the possibility that the recipient won't like the gift.</li>
        </ol>
        <p>In conclusion, an AI-powered gift suggestion tool offers a convenient, time-saving, and personalized solution for
        gift-giving. With the help of artificial intelligence, individuals can now find the perfect gift for their loved ones,
        ensuring that their gifts are well-received and appreciated.</p>
    </div>








    <script>
        const paragraphs = document.querySelectorAll(".intro p");
        const readTimeDiv = document.querySelector(".read-word");
        const count = document.querySelector(".count-word");

        const calculatedReadTime = () => {
            let numberOfWords = 0;
            const averageWPM = 265;

            paragraphs.forEach(paragraph => {
                numberOfWords += paragraph.innerHTML.split(" ").length;
            })

            let readTime = numberOfWords / averageWPM;

            readTimeDiv.innerHTML = Math.round(readTime) + " minute read"
            count.innerHTML = numberOfWords + " -words approximate"

        }
        calculatedReadTime();



    </script>

    {{>lowerlinks}}
</body>

</html>